TITLE: Connecting to Substrate Node and Using ChainHead RPC Methods in Rust
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create an RPC client connection to a local Substrate node, initialize the ChainHead RPC methods interface, and use a subscription to receive chainhead follow events. The example shows the basic pattern of establishing a connection and processing stream data.
